      <title>‘Plan B’ and the Bankruptcy of U.S. Syria Policy</title>
      <category domain="https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/diplomacy-foreign-affairs/">Diplomacy &amp; Foreign Affairs</category>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Mar 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Gareth Porter</author>
