      <guid>https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/community/2016/03/02/plan-b-and-the-bankruptcy-of-u-s-syria-policy</guid>
      <description>The United States has three “Plan B” options on the table if the peace process fails in Syria. None of them, according to investigative journalist Gareth Porter, is a winning idea. “If the U.S. policy were a company doing business in Syria,” he writes, “it would have gone bankrupt years ago”.</description>
